  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this non-interventional multicentre, prospective, observational cohort study, the efficacy
      of desmopressin is evaluated in patients with platelet dysfunction due to acetylsalicylic
      acid or cox-1-inhibitors within the context of surgical procedures.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
